reviews.review_text:
Peggy Pumped up Peggy!

What a difference from one of the gentlest on the 12th.
78' WV This gem of a show actually surprised me.Real nice Scarlet>Fire .

sublime well played, dynamic sounding tape. Certainly after listening to the tapes which warrant questions without much resolution, I am happy to say within the confines of 4/16/78 there are nothing but answers...beautiful renewed faith in the Grateful Dead cannon. Betty's tape is restored and beautiful here in true fashion...look no further, let the music play!
